title: Will Sparks
description:
Will Sparks, an Australian DJ and music producer, was born on March 15, 1993, in Melbourne, Australia.

In 2023, Will Sparks independently released his solo album ‘Accepted Concept,’ which has since garnered millions of streams. Assuming a pivotal role as the head of CLUBWRK, a distinguished sub-label under the umbrella of Teamwrk Records, Sparks seamlessly transitioned from DJ to Label Executive.

Beyond his successful music career, Sparks is a dynamic performer, gracing the stages of some of the world’s most prominent music festivals, including Tomorrowland, and Electric Daisy Carnival.

Ranked among the Top 100 DJs multiple times, Will Sparks continues to evolve and shape the electronic music landscape.
